These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-1::.
There 4 different types of food: lettuce, blueberry, nectarine, strawberry
The people have 4 different hobbies: singing, camping, drawing, fishing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, scientific, martial-arts, comedy
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, salsa, country, blues
4 different pets are kept: dog, snake, goldfish, fish
 1. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person eating blueberry##1
 2. the person who's hobby is camping is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
 3. the person who's hobby is fishing is on the left of the fan of salsa##1
 4. the owner of the snake is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
 5. the fan of pop is the person eating lettuce##1
 6. the fan of salsa is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
 7. the fan of country is on the right of the person eating lettuce##1
 8. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 9. the person watching martial-arts movies is the person eating lettuce##1
10. the owner of the goldfish is the person watching scientific movies##1
11. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the owner of the fish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3      |     4      |
| Food          | blueberry    | nectarine      | lettuce  | strawberry     |
| Hobby         | fishing    | drawing   | singing | camping      |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific       | adventure | martial-arts     | comedy    |
| Music-Genre   | blues | salsa         | pop  | country    |
| Pet           | goldfish      | fish       | dog | snake |

