.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, iced-tea, tea, almond-milk
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: sports, time-travel, martial-arts, comedy
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: soul, d&b, techno, country
4 different pets are kept: horse, dog, frog, lizard
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, baseball, climbing, surfing
 1. the person watching time-travel movies is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
 2. the fan of soul is on the right of the person who's sport is baseball##1
 3. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
 4. the person drinking almond-milk is on the far right##1
 5. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 6. the person who's sport is climbing is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
 7. the fan of country is on the right of the person watching sports movies##1
 8. the owner of the dog is the fan of country##1
 9. the person watching martial-arts movies is the fan of techno##1
10. the fan of soul is on the far right##1
11. the person drinking tea is on the left of the owner of the horse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3     |       4       |
| Beverage      | iced-tea      | water     | tea    | almond-milk |
| Movie-Genre   | sports | time-travel   | martial-arts   | comedy           |
| Music-Genre   | d&b  | country     | techno    | soul         |
| Pet           | lizard         | dog | frog     | horse        |
| Sport         | golf     | surfing  | baseball | climbing       |

