.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-3::.
There 4 different types of food: carrot, banana, pear, peach
There are 4 different nationalities: russian, italian, indian, turkish
4 different pets are kept: lizard, bird, guinea-pig, horse
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, volleyball, rugby, golf
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, snowmobile, taxi, helicopter
 1. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
 3. the person eating pear is the owner of the horse##1
 4. the person eating banana is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
 5. the person who's sport is rugby is on the right of the person eating peach##1
 6. the person driving the helicopter is the person eating pear##1
 7. the indian is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
 8. the person driving the motorbike is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
 9. the turkish is the owner of the bird##1
10. the italian is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
11. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
12. the person eating pear is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3    |       4       |
| Food          | carrot    | peach      | pear  | banana   |
| Nationality   | turkish     | indian      | italian | russian      |
| Pet           | bird       | lizard         | horse  | guinea-pig         |
| Sport         | cricket | volleyball | rugby  | golf |
| Transport     | taxi       | motorbike         | helicopter   | snowmobile        |

