.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: juice, iced-tea, milk, fanta
There 4 different types of food: peas, artichoke, pear, broccoli
There are 4 different nationalities: polish, french, egyptian, turkish
4 different pets are kept: mouse, bird, ferret, hedgehog
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, scooter, van, motorbike
 1. the owner of the bird is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
 2. the person eating broccoli is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
 3. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1
 4. the owner of the ferret is on the far right##1
 5. the person driving the bus is on the far left##1
 6. the person driving the van is on the left of the person drinking iced-tea##1
 7. the turkish is on the far right##1
 8. the person eating broccoli is on the right of the egyptian##1
 9. the french is on the left of the person eating peas##1
10. the person drinking juice is on the far right##1
11. the person drinking milk is on the far left##1
12. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person eating artichoke##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | milk   | fanta   | iced-tea      | juice     |
| Food          | pear     | peas   | broccoli | artichoke |
| Nationality   | french | egyptian | polish   | turkish       |
| Pet           | bird       | mouse      | hedgehog     | ferret |
| Transport     | bus    | van     | motorbike     | scooter     |

