 2. the person who's hobby is camping is on the far left##1
 3. the french is on the far right##1
 4. the owner of the goldfish is the person eating blueberry##1
 5. the owner of the goldfish is on the right of the person eating orange##1
 6. the nurse is on the far right##1
 7. the owner of the turtle is on the right of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
 8. the owner of the rat is the police-officer##1
 9. the person eating pomegranate is the owner of the turtle##1
10. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
11. the british is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
12. the designer is on the far left##1
13. the british is on the right of the person who's hobby is writing##1
14. the brazilian is on the right of the indonesian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3      |    4     |
