.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-6::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: video-games, filmmaking, reading, chess
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: scientific, horror, disaster, mystery
There are 4 different nationalities: turkish, german, american, chinese
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: basketball, rowing, parkour, biathlon
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, roller, snowmobile, quad-bike
 1. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the american##1
 2. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 3. the person who's hobby is chess is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 4. the person watching horror movies is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 5. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the turkish##1
 6. the turkish is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 7. the person driving the snowmobile is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 8. the person who's sport is basketball is on the left of the turkish##1
 9. the german is on the far right##1
10. the person who's sport is parkour is the person driving the quad-bike##1
11. the person who's hobby is reading is the person watching scientific movies##1
12. the american is the person driving the helicopter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |      3       |      4      |
| Hobby         | filmmaking   | reading | chess    | video-games  |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery    | scientific | disaster      | horror |
| Nationality   | american | turkish | chinese         | german  |
| Sport         | basketball  | parkour     | biathlon | rowing     |
| Transport     | helicopter      | quad-bike       | snowmobile         | roller         |

