The people prefer 4 different types of sport: water-polo, skateboarding, golf, soccer
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, quad-bike, train, ship
 1. the teacher is on the right of the person who's sport is golf##1
 2. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far left##1
 3. the person driving the boat is the person who's sport is golf##1
 4. the person drinking fanta is on the far left##1
 5. the teacher is the person who's sport is skateboarding##1
 6. the person drinking tea is the person driving the ship##1
 7. the person who's hobby is traveling is the person driving the quad-bike##1
 8. the person drinking 7up is the chef##1
 9. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person driving the quad-bike##1
10. the person who's sport is water-polo is the person drinking fanta##1
11. the librarian is on the left of the chef##1
12. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the person driving the boat##1
13. the person drinking 7up is on the right of the person driving the train##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |      3       |       4       |
