| Hobby       | card-games    | board-games        | gardening  | hiking      |
| Job         | lawyer  | police-officer | social-worker | nurse |
| Pet         | fish | guinea-pig          | rat         | hedgehog      |
| Transport   | quad-bike     | train     | roller       | taxi          |

