.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: tea, coffee, almond-milk, cola
The people have 4 different hobbies: skydiving, chess, baking, card-games
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: martial-arts, horror, action, comedy
There are 4 different nationalities: egyptian, german, malaysian, colombian
4 different pets are kept: hamster, fish, pony, rabbit
 1. the malaysian is on the far left##1
 2. the person drinking coffee is the person watching comedy movies##1
 3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the owner of the hamster##1
 4. the colombian is on the left of the egyptian##1
 5. the person who's hobby is baking is the person drinking almond-milk##1
 6. the person who's hobby is card-games is the person drinking cola##1
 7. the person who's hobby is chess is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
 8. the egyptian is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
 9. the owner of the fish is the person watching action movies##1
10. the person watching action movies is on the far left##1
11. the person drinking tea is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
12. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person watching horror movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |      3       |    4     |
| Beverage      | cola       | almond-milk      | coffee      | tea    |
| Hobby         | card-games | baking | chess | skydiving  |
| Movie-Genre   | action    | horror     | comedy      | martial-arts |
| Nationality   | malaysian  | colombian     | egyptian    | german  |
| Pet           | fish  | rabbit       | hamster          | pony      |

