.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-19::.
There 4 different types of food: pepper, blueberry, artichoke, nectarine
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, woodworking, sudoku, photography
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: spy, thriller, fantasy, epic
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, golf, cricket, basketball
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, car, tram, skateboard
 1. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far left##1
 2. the person eating nectarine is on the left of the person who's hobby is gardening##1
 3. the person driving the tram is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
 4. the person watching fantasy movies is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
 5. the person watching spy movies is on the left of the person driving the skateboard##1
 6. the person watching epic movies is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
 7. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person eating pepper##1
 8. the person who's sport is basketball is on the right of the person eating pepper##1
 9. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person eating blueberry##1
10. the person who's sport is basketball is the person eating artichoke##1
11. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person eating nectarine##1
12. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the far right##1
13. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the person driving the skateboard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |      3      |       4       |
| Food          | nectarine      | blueberry     | pepper        | artichoke     |
| Hobby         | sudoku     | gardening    | photography | woodworking |
| Movie-Genre   | spy | fantasy  | thriller      | epic       |
| Sport         | cricket      | surfing | golf     | basketball        |
| Transport     | tram   | skateboard     | taxi  | car       |

