.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-20::.
There 4 different types of food: papaya, potato, watermelon, apple
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, drawing, chess, collecting
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, teacher, bartender, designer
4 different pets are kept: rat, hamster, rabbit, bird
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, boat, van, airplane
 1. the designer is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 2. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the person eating papaya##1
 3. the designer is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
 4. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the fisherman##1
 5. the owner of the rabbit is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
 6. the person eating watermelon is on the right of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 7. the person driving the boat is on the right of the teacher##1
 8. the fisherman is the person driving the quad-bike##1
 9. the person eating watermelon is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1
10. the person eating apple is the owner of the bird##1
11. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person driving the van##1
12. the owner of the bird is on the left of the bartender##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |       3        |      4      |
| Food        | potato    | apple        | papaya        | watermelon      |
| Hobby       | chess       | woodworking       | drawing      | collecting |
| Job         | teacher | designer | bartender | fisherman      |
| Pet         | rat          | bird         | hamster           | rabbit    |
| Transport   | van         | boat       | airplane     | quad-bike   |

 